poly_attn: There is an unlimited amount of love, and loving someone does not take away from loving someone else. People need community to thrive, it's natural to love more than one person.

monog_attn: I think for some people, it works. Some people don't want to just have one long term partner. They need variety and some people just feel like multiple people can meet all of their needs. I don't fully understand it and I wouldn't want a relationship like that, but I do know it works well for some people.
Some people may be comfortable in a consensual relationship with more than one partner. Each relationship may match a different need or desire.
